{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2af37bd86","title":"毛泽东接见军队领导干部时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a71d6dde3e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"a2af37bd86"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f18c213523","type":"title","text":"接见军队领导干部时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"b0afec4424","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"49281265b1","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕闹，闹得越大、越长，越好。七闹八闹，总会闹出名堂来的，可以闹清楚。不管怎么闹，不要怕，越怕鬼越来。但也不要开枪，什么时候开枪也是不好的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"9e4456d536","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大闹不可能。那里有脓包，有细菌，总要爆发的。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"88344603e1","type":"paragraph","text":"南京街上闹得很厉害，我越看越高兴。闹得第三派那么多人，反对内战，反对武斗，这很好嘛！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"9b16c17c6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：有人讲第三派是走第三条道路的。）","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"},{"id":"14ae9af24a","type":"paragraph","text":"哪有什么第三条道路呀！人家要大联合，大批判，你要诱导嘛！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86"}],"page":{"id":"e725dc4e00","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2af37bd86","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}